---
title: Sweet Chilli Pork Burger with Sesame Fries & Rainbow Slaw
description: Burgers and fries, you know all about them, right? Wrong! This juicy pork patty gets a sweet chilli glaze, while the baked potato fries have a sprinkling of toasted sesame seeds to jazz up their flavour. Plus, a rainbow coleslaw with a garlicky dressing takes the salad portion of the meal to new heights. Enjoy the tastiest lesson around as you get to know this new take on the family favourite.
